      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was conducted on the screw shank and rod interface regions. The Grid Convergence Index for construct stiffness was 2.8% and for yield force was 3.1%, both below the 5% threshold. The medium mesh (approximately 420,000 elements) was adopted for production runs."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
