      "rationale": "Experimental boundary conditions (grip fixture geometry, actuator displacement rate) were replicated in the FEA model. CMM-measured screw and rod dimensions were used directly as model inputs. Remaining discrepancies (e.g., assembly torque variability) were quantified and incorporated into the combined validation uncertainty uval."
