      "acceptanceCriteria": "Comparison metric E/uval < 1.96 for all three QoIs across both laboratories; relative difference < 10%.",
      "rationale": "All six QoI-laboratory combinations satisfy both acceptance criteria. Maximum E/uval is 1.61 (force at 40 mm, Lab 2), below the 1.96 threshold. Maximum relative difference is 5.9% (force at 40 mm, Lab 2), below the 10% threshold. The model is judged validated for the stated COU."
